---

<BaseLayout
  title="Upcoming Features - Spentiva by Exyconn"
  description="See what's coming next to Spentiva. Get early access to new features like WhatsApp integration, bank statement analysis, bill splitting, and more."
>
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero Section with Premium Gradient -->
  <section
